  "texts": [
    "Another potential cause for concern could be that the models we used may not be the best, or at least not the best suited for the task performed.",
    "It is true that in a rapidly changing landscape, it is often difficult to remain up to date.",
    "In fact, in the course of this research, we reran our experiments frequently, either due to new versions of models being released, or due to an entirely new model emerging as the new \"state of the art\" (see Appendix B.1).",
    "We only report the most recent version tested for each model.",
    "Still, we believe that our strategy yields solid results to date."
  ],
